For cross-compiling, you need to override PM2_ARCH, PM2_ASM, PM2_CC (and even
PM2_SYS if needed):

For instance, for compiling x86_64 binaries on x86:

PM2_AR=ar
PM2_CC=gcc -m64
PM2_ARCH=X86_64_ARCH
PM2_ASM=x86_64
export PM2_CC PM2_ARCH PM2_ASM PM2_AR

And for compiling PPC64 binaries on AIX:

PM2_AR=ar -X64
PM2_CC=gcc -maix64 -mcpu=powerpc64
PM2_ARCH=PPC64_ARCH
PM2_ASM=ppc64
export PM2_CC PM2_ARCH PM2_ASM PM2_AR
